In the midst of a career change and expecting my first kid in a couple weeks, so I thought it was only right to dust off my Net54 account and treat myself to a new card in celebration.

Looking for a low grade American Beauty. This is for my back set, so I would actually prefer a cleaner looking back over the artwork, but open to seeing any and and all offers.

Thanks!
